name: DESPONDENCY
description: A 1.9 Denouement remake, where a near-impossible wave at the start, and a tough but doable wave at the end, make up all of the difficulty, with basic cube and ship gameplay in between. Straight from hell.
gdleveldescription: 753 attempts and like 5 deaths to the last wave. Funny denouement style level. GL!
author: Raezori
